Pre-Game Insights: Chipolopolo are going all out this evening against Morocco in their must-win and final 2023 AFCON Group F match at Stade Laurent Pokou in San Pedro.
Zambia is eager to redeem itself after a 1-1 draw in their opening two Group F fixtures against DR Congo and Tanzania.
There is still a lot of fight in this team according to Musonda.
